            <p><strong><a href="http://searchengineland.com/70-consumers-will-leave-review-business-asked-262802" target="_blank">70% of Consumers Will Leave a Review for a Business When Asked</a></strong></p>
            <p>BrightLocal reported in its 2016 Local Consumer Review Survey that consumers are increasingly using the Internet to find local businesses and select which business to patronize based on online reviews. Accordingly, businesses must optimize their online presence in their local markets by soliciting online reviews. The survey also revealed that approximately 70% of respondents said they will leave a review for a business if they’ve been asked to do so, making this a useful strategy to raise a business’s online profile.</p>
