            <p><strong><a href="https://techcrunch.com/2016/11/07/jobbook/" target="_blank">Facebook Threatens LinkedIn With Job Opening Features</a></strong></p>
            <p>Facebook may be looking to compete with LinkedIn with the advent of options to list available job opportunities on Facebook Business Pages. Business owners may now see a ‘Jobs’ tab on their Facebook Page, and Facebook has also recently confirmed that it is evaluating the effectiveness of several different recruiting features that may ultimately rival those on LinkedIn.</p>
